Bug Fixes: Fixed a bug that caused playback to crash on some devices over poor connections
Fixes: Fixed a bug that prevented the correct episode from playing for a series with many episodes Improvements: Improved crash logging and error handling
New Features: Improved in app analytics that will allow us to deliver content tailored to your preferences.

Bug Fixes: Fixed a bug that prevented users from reattempting sign in after entering incorrect credentials Fixed a crash that occurred when a user would play a media item while recommended media is loading Fixed a bug that prevented users from seeing their account history properly
Bug Fix: Fixed a bug that made it difficult to find the button to enable Closed Captions when playing media full screen .

New Features: Recommended programs now autoplay You can now choose the Kids Mode setting to hide content that is not child friendly Fixes Improvements: Search is a bit smoother Fixed some Chromecast bugs You can now back out of the subscription purchase flow

New Features: Search is now easier just tap on the Search icon in the header to find content! Bug Fixes: Fixed a bug that prevented users from resuming a video Fixed a bug that prevented users from viewing Collections properly
Fixed a bug that prevented all of the sections from being presented in Home
Fixed a bug that caused a crash after the last episode of a series Minor additions for better analytics UI fixes
Minor bug fixes and improvements for media playback
Fixed a bug where the app would crash on some devices when opening a series Minor UI tweaks and bug fixes
More UI updates Now you can browse our Collections! You can now search and browse for our content from your Apple TV s main search and Siri.
New features: Purchase a subscription via In App Purchases!
New features: Updated app store information with new theme
New features: New theme! Minor bug fixes.
New features: Chromecast support Closed captions support
Bug fixes: Landscape mode playback on iPhones Dismissal of playback controls Other minor fixes
This version includes a number of bug fixes: Fixed: Background AirPlay Fixed: Playback resume Fixed: Error messages when no network is detected Other minor fixes
Additions: Icons for iPad Pro Fixes: Bug in Settings where About Terms and Conditions Privacy Policy would not load properly
Fixed a few minor issues regarding text.
Video Series: Now watch entire series on your iPhone iPad. AirPlay: Enjoy videos on your TV with full Apple TV AirPlay support.
